text: Ernest Hawełek (born 28 January 1935) is a Polish gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Poland Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Wodzisław County Category:Sportspeople from Silesian Voivodeship
